        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and served Baal; which was service to the sun, as Abarbinel interprets it; this was the god of the Zidonians Ahab worshipped, having married a princess of that people, 1 Kings 16:31. ",
        "children": [
          {
